<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>{{subject}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .auction-details {
      background-color: #fff5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
    }
    .time-remaining {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #e74c3c;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Hurry! Auction Ending Soon</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
    
    <p>This is a friendly reminder that the auction you're watching is ending soon!</p>
    
    <div class="auction-details">
      <h2>{{title}}</h2>
      <p class="time-remaining">⏰ Ends in less than {{timeRemaining}}!</p>
      <p><strong>Current Bid:</strong> ${{currentBid}}</p>
      <p><strong>Your Max Bid:</strong> ${{maxBid}}</p>
      <p><strong>Ends:</strong> {{formatDate endTime}}</p>
      
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/auctions/{{auctionId}}" class="button">Place a Higher Bid Now</a>
    </div>
    
    <p>Don't miss out on this item! If you're still interested, now is the time to place a higher bid.</p>
    
    <p>Good luck with your bidding!</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>© {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/unsubscribe" style="color: #777; text-decoration: underline;">Unsubscribe from auction reminders</a> | 
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/account/notifications" style="color: #777; text-decoration: underline;">Manage notifications</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
